    Area
    Class Area contains the possible object that could be available to an area.

    Class Bank handles the balance of the current instance of a bank, Further, it handles any deposits and withdraws made by Players as long as there are sufficient resources.

    Brown card is a type of Card.

    GreenCard
    Green card is a type of Card.
